I’m not sure I ever expected to pick up the Sunday funnies and see jokes about data center power and cooling. But yesterday’s Dilbert is all about “hot spots” - and what might happen if the Pointy-Haired Boss was in charge of decisions about data center design. Of course, that would never happen at your company. Right?
We’ve had to shrink the strip to embed it here, but you’ll want to click through to Dilbert.com (Beta) to see the full-size cartoon.